ght while serving to direct readers to the corpus of Rescher's writings for amore complete picture.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aPhilosophy, Modern. 0aPhilosophy. 4aLogik. 4aMetaphysik. 4aNicholas Rescher. 4aPhilosophie. 4aWissenschaftstheorie. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh1 aAlmeder, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoodman, Lenn E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreco, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacquette, Dale, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacquette, Dale, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aJaworski, William, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPuntel, Lorenz B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoods, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Philosophy 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023848808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook Package De Gruyter Ontos 2002-2012z978311033122608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook Paket De Gruyter Ontos 2002-2012z9783110331219oZDB-23-DON0 cprintz978311032866040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311032905640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110329056423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110329056/original  a978-3-11-023848-8  DGBA Backlist Philosophy 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-